Klipspringer Primary’s grade one learners looked happy to be in their classrooms. As a precautionary measure in line with Covid-19 safety protocol, schools are using different timetables. According to these timetables, pupils’ attendance is alternated on different days or weeks suitable to the needs of each school.    Here are some of the learners who started school today:            ALSO SEE IN PHOTOS: White River Primary’s grade ones are not camera-shy